title: etnies x Cinema in Portland
description: The ETNIES & CINEMA BMX teams joined forces for another summertime adventure, this time in Portland, Oregon. Corey Martinez, Chase Dehart and Nathan Williams all ride for both etnies and CINEMA so it makes sense for both brands to collab on filming trips
